00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:06.260
mad with technical development.

00:04:06.340 --> 00:04:07.580
What do I mean with this?

00:04:08.020 --> 00:04:09.500
And it is something very usual.

00:04:09.600 --> 00:04:12.000
If you are an entrepreneur, you are

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:13.020
sure to be identified.

00:04:13.060 --> 00:04:14.780
Especially entrepreneurs whose

00:04:14.780 --> 00:04:18.580
proposals require or are balanced

00:04:18.580 --> 00:04:20.780
on a website, on a platform,

00:04:20.780 --> 00:04:23.340
in an application, etc.

00:04:23.420 --> 00:04:25.380
The usual thing is that, especially

00:04:25.380 --> 00:04:27.560
entrepreneurs who are not experts

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:30.000
in the technical area, they find

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:31.280
a world of creating the website

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:32.160
and creating the platform.

00:04:32.320 --> 00:04:33.860
And from the beginning what they

00:04:33.860 --> 00:04:34.940
do is look for a supplier and put

00:04:34.940 --> 00:04:36.600
themselves in the hands of an agency

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:37.960
or a programmer, etc., which seems

00:04:37.960 --> 00:04:39.160
to become the most important person

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:40.080
in the company during the

00:04:40.080 --> 00:04:40.820
first months.

00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:44.680
And all the effort, all the focus

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:46.060
and all the budget goes there

00:04:46.060 --> 00:04:47.940
to create the website.

00:04:48.060 --> 00:04:49.160
It is ridiculous, I tell you, it is

00:04:49.200 --> 00:04:50.240
ridiculous, don't do it.

00:04:50.400 --> 00:04:51.400
What you have to do at first

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:53.660
is, the most important thing is to validate

00:04:53.660 --> 00:04:54.840
that that you are building, there

00:04:54.840 --> 00:04:57.820
is someone who wants to buy it,

00:04:57.820 --> 00:04:59.740
someone sees value and in addition

00:04:59.740 --> 00:05:01.380
that that feedback incorporates

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:03.040
it into the product development.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:05.500
And the least important thing is how

00:05:05.500 --> 00:05:07.200
to give it a solution, really, because

00:05:07.200 --> 00:05:08.160
that is a commodity.

00:05:09.540 --> 00:05:11.160
The important thing, what creates true

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:13.880
value is that you are able to identify

00:05:13.880 --> 00:05:16.100
something or be able to create

00:05:16.100 --> 00:05:17.380
something that people want to buy.

00:05:19.160 --> 00:05:21.420
The technical specifications

00:05:21.420 --> 00:05:23.000
are much less important, don'

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:24.100
t focus on that, don'

00:05:24.100 --> 00:05:24.960
t wear it off.

