about here is, they're tips related

00:05:30.780 --> 00:05:32.620
to partners, the team, etc.,

00:05:32.820 --> 00:05:33.960
with whom to surround you.

00:05:34.880 --> 00:05:37.400
The first is to find a partner.

00:05:37.400 --> 00:05:37.940


00:05:38.900 --> 00:05:40.760
It is very hard to be an entrepreneur

00:05:40.760 --> 00:05:43.480
if you are alone and if we think

00:05:43.480 --> 00:05:44.880
of the main ones, we can think of

00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:46.220
the main exits in recent years

00:05:46.220 --> 00:05:48.340
in Spain, almost all, are at

00:05:48.340 --> 00:05:50.420
least two or more co-founders.

00:05:50.620 --> 00:05:51.340
Why is?

00:05:51.340 --> 00:05:52.660
For several reasons, first because there

00:05:52.660 --> 00:05:54.920
are many bad days in which having partners

00:05:54.920 --> 00:05:57.240
helps you and also because it is very

00:05:57.240 --> 00:05:58.920
difficult, except that you are superman,

00:05:59.180 --> 00:06:00.280
that you have all the abilities,

00:06:00.280 --> 00:06:01.720
all the competencies, that you

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:03.060
are a leader, good communicator,

00:06:03.060 --> 00:06:04.420
visionary, you understand the

00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:05.700
business, you understand the networking,

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:06.720
you understand the money, it

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:07.780
is very complicated.

00:06:08.700 --> 00:06:09.740
Instead, it is much easier than

00:06:09.740 --> 00:06:11.580
between two or three or four

00:06:11.580 --> 00:06:13.980
people, maybe four is too

00:06:13.980 --> 00:06:18.340
much, all those competences are combined.

00:06:18.980 --> 00:06:21.260
In addition, the choice of those

00:06:21.260 --> 00:06:22.440
partners is very important and in

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:24.220
many cases the partners are chosen without

00:06:24.220 --> 00:06:25.120
thinking.

00:06:25.540 --> 00:06:26.940
It seems to be done naturally.

00:06:27.940 --> 00:06:31.000
But you really have to make

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:32.920
this decision very reasonably.

00:06:33.700 --> 00:06:35.800
And one of the recommendations of the

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:36.880
advice I have heard from many successful

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:38.280
entrepreneurs, that in addition if we

00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:40.640
analyze them is so, it is that people

00:06:41.020 --> 00:06:44.380
have been associated that complement

00:06:44.380 --> 00:06:45.760
themselves.

00:06:45.760 --> 00:06:47.120
What do I mean by this?

00:06:47.460 --> 00:06:48.840
People who have different competencies,

00:06:48.840 --> 00:06:51.000
because one is more technical and

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:52.780
the other is more focused on business,

00:06:52.780 --> 00:06:54.260
one is more commercial and the

00:06:54.260 --> 00:06:55.740
other is more executive,

00:06:55.740 --> 00:06:57.080
I don't know.

00:06:58.160 --> 00:06:59.760
But they come together, they generate

00:06:59.760 --> 00:07:01.340
those synergies and it is also important,

00:07:01.480 --> 00:07:03.340
another factor that is important, and

00:07:03.340 --> 00:07:05.160
is that each person likes to do different

00:07:05.160 --> 00:07:06.680
things.

00:07:06.740 --> 00:07:07.940
Because there is one that likes

00:07:07.940 --> 00:07:09.260
to manage teams more and the other

00:07:09.260 --> 00:07:10.540
likes to sell and be in events,

00:07:10.540 --> 00:07:11.720
be in the saras, well.

00:07:11.980 --> 00:07:14.400
But this is important because I

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:16.200
have met cases of entrepreneurs

00:07:16.200 --> 00:07:18.260
who were very similar in the

00:07:18.260 --> 00:07:19.420
end, they understood each other

00:07:19.420 --> 00:07:20.100
well but they were too

00:07:20.100 --> 00:07:21.860
similar and both liked doing the

00:07:21.860 --> 00:07:22.560
same thing.

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:24.360
And they were not generating value,

00:07:24.440 --> 00:07:25.500
they were destroying value, there was

00:07:25.500 --> 00:07:26.580
a duplicity.

00:07:27.620 --> 00:07:30.640
Another unromantic recommendation

00:07:30.640 --> 00:07:33.560
is that things stay very clear and

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:35.080
written from the first day.

00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:36.420
I know you won't do this because

00:07:36.420 --> 00:07:39.520
people of that and this advice.

00:07:39.560 --> 00:07:41.240
