00:07:41.240 --> 00:07:44.080
spend five minutes or less thinking

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:48.980
about cases close to you of entrepreneurs

00:07:48.980 --> 00:07:50.220
or entrepreneurs who have discussed

00:07:50.220 --> 00:07:52.440
with their partners, it's super

00:07:52.440 --> 00:07:53.160
common.

00:07:53.760 --> 00:07:54.700
Why is?

00:07:54.820 --> 00:07:55.800
Well, because things, first

00:07:55.900 --> 00:07:56.700
because decisions were

00:07:56.700 --> 00:07:58.240
made without thinking too much

00:07:58.240 --> 00:08:00.580
and also not established in

00:08:00.580 --> 00:08:01.080
writing.

00:08:01.540 --> 00:08:02.960
Relationships usually

00:08:02.960 --> 00:08:05.360
last for many years,

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:06.460
good times, bad times

00:08:06.460 --> 00:08:08.200
and opportunities

00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:10.240
to discuss are countless.

00:08:10.460 --> 00:08:11.900
Take it into account.

00:08:12.660 --> 00:08:15.440
Another recommendation is that, I said

00:08:15.440 --> 00:08:16.840
before, you are looking for a partner, looking

00:08:16.840 --> 00:08:18.020
for one or several partners, but what

00:08:18.020 --> 00:08:20.180
