00:09:16.500 --> 00:09:17.620
In the end, what will happen is

00:09:17.620 --> 00:09:19.000
that you will have such a small percentage

00:09:19.000 --> 00:09:20.440
of the company that it won't

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:21.140
be worth it.

00:09:21.980 --> 00:09:23.220
You will lose motivation

