00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:17.280
recommendations is hurried off.

00:11:17.280 --> 00:11:19.620
Sometimes it's hard, to say goodbye

00:11:19.620 --> 00:11:20.580
is very hard, but you really have

00:11:20.580 --> 00:11:22.660
to be inflexible about it when

00:11:22.660 --> 00:11:23.960
you identify that there are people

00:11:23.960 --> 00:11:25.580
inside your team that don't fit within

00:11:25.580 --> 00:11:27.280
the culture or that don't share

00:11:27.280 --> 00:11:27.980
values, etc.

00:11:28.040 --> 00:11:29.800
It is best to fired him as soon

00:11:29.800 --> 00:11:30.620
