00:12:29.520 --> 00:12:31.340
productivity, a lot of initiative.

00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:33.780
You can't hire profiles that

00:12:33.780 --> 00:12:34.960
are waiting for you to tell

00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:35.480
you what to do.

00:12:35.580 --> 00:12:36.580
You have to hire profiles that arrive

00:12:36.580 --> 00:12:37.720
