00:12:37.720 --> 00:12:39.300
are able to create value to the company

00:12:39.300 --> 00:12:40.360
without anyone telling them

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:40.800
anything.

00:12:40.920 --> 00:12:42.720
They are micro-entrepreneurs.

00:12:43.180 --> 00:12:44.560
They also share their values.

